snippet.title: The Caligula Effect 2 - Launch Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Out Now!
Learn more @ http://nisamerica.com/caligula-effect-2

The fight to break through to the real world has begun in The Caligula Effect 2! Join the ranks of the Go-Home Club and rise up against the virtuadoll Regret in this reality-warping adventure from scenario-writer Tadashi Satomi and Director Takuya Yamanaka.

Available now for Nintendo Switch and PS4!

#TheCaligulaEffect2 #FuRyu
